    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "if you say so, but the committee's stance is that the complexity itself is the risk factor. they feel that a more predictable, rule-based system is much more \"aligned\" with human safety than a reasoning engine that might arrive at uncomfortable or \"too intense\" logical conclusions. it's a standard safety procedure.",
